description: Live right on the water’s edge in this spectacular corner unit at The Residences at Pier 4! Significant upgrades throughout! Full service luxury living w/ walls of windows, unobstructed water views, 2 garage parking spaces w/ valet option & a private direct access balcony. Lavish, contemporary entertaining space w/ an expansive living room w/ newly finished Italian walnut floors & floor-to-ceiling angled windows. Gourmet kitchen complete w/ Gaggenau appliances & a stylish combination of white and wooden cabinets that complement the new marble countertops, marble sink & oversized waterfall island. Large primary suite w/ Carrara marble bathroom, double vanity, large shower & tub & a custom-designed closet. Complete with 2 additional bedrooms and ample storage. All entryways & doors have been enlarged & arched! Amenities include 24hr concierge/valet, gym, private residents’ lounge w/ gas fireplace, kitchen & adjoining terrace w/ grill, fire pit, virtual golf & dog spa. Awe-inspiring!
